```python
import random

# 计算每个员工名字在所有员工名字中出现的次数
employee_names = ["蔡承恩", "陳文雄", "林雅婷", "李淑英", "张海燕", "林秀美", "王建平", "馬秀英", "王小桂", "王小妹", "张淑芬", "李兰英", "刘红梅", "刘玉梅", "张桂珍", "蔡承翰", "黃淑惠", "陳宥萜", "李俊毅"]
employee_name_count = {}
for name in employee_names:
    employee_name_count[name] = 0

for name in employee_names:
    employee_name_count[name] += 1

# 计算每个员工名字的得分
employee_scores = {}
for name in employee_names:
    employee_scores[name] = employee_name_count[name] / len(employee_names)

# 对得分进行降序排列，选出得分最高的员工
sorted_scores = sorted(employee_scores.items(), key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)

# 输出结果
print("排名前10的员工名字：")
for i, score in enumerate(sorted_scores[:10]):
    print(f"{i+1}. {score[0]}: {score[1]}")
```
